'''Tōdaiji Yōroku''' (東大寺要録) is a temple chronicle of {{ill|Tōdai-ji|ja|東大寺|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, compiled in the late {{ill|Heian period|ja|平安時代|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. It consists of 10 volumes divided into 10 chapters.
